29:00.113 --> 29:01.156
 <i>Please.</i>

29:05.910 --> 29:07.328
 <i>Is there a nice doctor</i>
 <i>I can call</i>

29:07.370 --> 29:09.247
 <i>who can tell me</i>
 <i>you're not a serial killer?</i>

29:10.790 --> 29:11.833
 <i>No.</i>

29:13.293 --> 29:15.211
 <i>Why didn't you just shoot me</i>
 <i>and take my truck?</i>

29:15.253 --> 29:17.422
 <i>You are...</i>

29:20.592 --> 29:21.926
 <i>necessary.</i>

29:31.311 --> 29:33.062
 <i>[Faraday gasps softly]</i>

29:36.816 --> 29:38.651
 <i>Where is the fluid sac?</i>

29:40.153 --> 29:41.654
 <i>Excuse me?</i>

29:41.696 --> 29:45.450
 <i>I travel in a fluid sac.</i>

29:47.368 --> 29:48.495
 <i>Yeah.</i>

29:48.536 --> 29:50.955
 <i>[woman speaking indistinctly</i>
 <i>on radio]</i>

29:50.997 --> 29:52.123
 <i>What's your name?</i>

29:53.333 --> 29:55.293
 <i>[Faraday] K. Faraday.</i>

29:55.794 --> 29:56.961
 <i>[Justin] Faraday?</i>

29:58.755 --> 29:59.798
 <i>[radio tuning]</i>

29:59.839 --> 30:01.633
 <i>Okay, don't...</i>
 <i>Don't play with my radio.</i>

30:03.676 --> 30:05.303
 <i>[radio tuning]</i>

30:05.345 --> 30:07.472
 <i>Stop. What'd I just say?</i>

30:07.514 --> 30:09.057
 <i>Stop! Stop.</i>

30:09.974 --> 30:11.643
 <i>You stopped work.</i>

30:11.684 --> 30:13.269
 <i>-Why did you stop?</i>
 <i>-No.</i>

30:13.311 --> 30:14.479
 <i>I'm not engaging</i>
 <i>with you, okay?</i>

30:14.521 --> 30:16.231
 <i>Why did you stop?</i>

30:16.272 --> 30:20.276
 <i>Did the plasma disruptions</i>
 <i>become too substantial?</i>

30:20.318 --> 30:22.278
 <i>[song playing on radio]</i>

30:22.320 --> 30:24.614
 <i>Okay. All right. New rule.</i>

30:24.656 --> 30:27.659
 <i>You can play with the radio,</i>
 <i>so long as you don't talk.</i>

30:27.700 --> 30:29.994
 <i>Did you miscalculate</i>
 <i>the stored energy</i>

30:30.036 --> 30:31.037
 <i>in the plasma engine?</i>

30:31.079 --> 30:32.664
 <i>I didn't miscalculate.</i>

30:33.665 --> 30:35.291
 <i>I got it wrong.</i>

30:35.333 --> 30:37.669
 <i>Nothing on Earth can sustain</i>
 <i>that much energy.</i>

30:37.710 --> 30:39.504
 <i>Nothing on Earth.</i>

30:44.884 --> 30:46.678
 <i>Yeah. [scoffs]</i>

30:46.719 --> 30:49.597
 <i>I'm not... I'm not gonna</i>
 <i>engage with you on this.</i>

30:51.266 --> 30:52.475
 <i>[scoffs]</i>

30:54.727 --> 30:55.812
 <i>Hey.</i>

30:57.105 --> 30:58.189
 <i>Hey!</i>

31:00.900 --> 31:04.112
 <i>[whispering] Fuck me. [sighs]</i>

31:08.241 --> 31:09.367
 <i>[phone keys clacking]</i>

31:10.076 --> 31:11.661
 <i>[line ringing]</i>

31:11.703 --> 31:13.788
 <i>-[Josiah on phone]</i> <i>Juzzie.</i>
 <i>-Hey, Dad!</i>

31:13.830 --> 31:16.708
<i>You all right? Huh?</i>
 <i>-No, no, I'm fine. I'm fine.</i>

31:16.749 --> 31:20.295
 <i>Yeah, I got something going.</i>
 <i>I can pay Marcus in cash.</i>

31:20.336 --> 31:21.629
 <i>[Josiah]</i> <i>Marcus was late.</i>

31:21.671 --> 31:23.339
<i>When are you coming home?</i>
<i>You coming home?</i>

31:23.381 --> 31:27.010
 <i>Look, Dad...</i>
 <i>Dad, it's gonna be okay.</i>

31:27.051 --> 31:30.847
 <i>I got something going.</i>
 <i>It's gonna buy us some time.</i>

31:30.889 --> 31:35.059
 <i>[Josiah]</i> <i>My hands are aching.</i>
<i>I need my pills.</i>

31:36.769 --> 31:38.855
 <i>[energy hums]</i>

31:38.897 --> 31:41.107
 <i>[electrical crackling]</i>

31:46.654 --> 31:48.698
 <i>[motorcycle engine revving]</i>

32:00.793 --> 32:01.878
 <i>Why did you stop?</i>

32:02.712 --> 32:04.213
 <i>We have five hours...</i>

32:04.255 --> 32:05.882
 <i>For gas.</i>

32:06.716 --> 32:08.051
 <i>For gas?</i>

32:08.092 --> 32:10.094
 <i>["Calaveras County"</i>
 <i>playing on radio]</i>

32:12.639 --> 32:14.015
 <i>[Faraday grunting]</i>

32:15.558 --> 32:18.019
<i>There's a quiet in the air </i>

32:18.061 --> 32:21.272
<i>There's a breeze</i>
<i>Off of the mountains </i>

32:21.314 --> 32:25.276
<i>And there's room for a man</i>
<i>To be his own </i>

32:25.318 --> 32:30.281
<i>Ain't no strangers</i>
<i>Here in Calaveras County... </i>

32:30.823 --> 32:32.116
 <i>Oh.</i>

32:34.118 --> 32:35.119
 <i>[grunts]</i>

32:47.173 --> 32:49.050
 <i>Is your friend</i>
 <i>committing suicide?</i>

32:51.135 --> 32:52.637
 <i>I have no idea.</i>

32:53.680 --> 32:55.431
 <i>If he's still alive,</i>

32:55.473 --> 32:57.308
 <i>will you tell him</i>
 <i>I'm getting a Snickers?</i>

32:59.310 --> 33:01.312
 <i>Buddy.</i>

33:01.354 --> 33:04.023
 <i>-[muffled] Buddy. Buddy.</i>
 <i>-[water gurgling]</i>

33:04.065 --> 33:05.274
 <i>[muffled] What?</i>

33:05.316 --> 33:06.818
 <i>["Calaveras County"</i>
 <i>continues playing]</i>

33:06.859 --> 33:08.194
 <i>You can't.</i>

33:08.236 --> 33:10.113
 <i>I'm buying that.</i>

33:10.154 --> 33:11.406
 <i>[dog barking]</i>

33:11.447 --> 33:13.282
 <i>-[cattle bells clanging]</i>
 <i>-[goats bleating]</i>

33:22.208 --> 33:23.710
 <i>[car horn blaring]</i>

33:29.215 --> 33:30.925
 <i>[horse whinnying]</i>

33:32.885 --> 33:34.554
 <i>[horse huffing]</i>

33:35.471 --> 33:37.348
 <i> pensive music </i>

33:38.850 --> 33:39.934
 <i>[horse whinnies]</i>

33:43.563 --> 33:44.814
 <i>[fly buzzes]</i>

33:44.856 --> 33:47.358
 <i>[horse snorting]</i>

33:56.534 --> 33:57.994
 <i>Hey, you wanna move away.</i>

33:58.036 --> 33:59.912
 <i>She's skittish,</i>
 <i>and I'm working.</i>

33:59.954 --> 34:01.330
 <i>[Justin] Yeah, two bottles.</i>

34:01.372 --> 34:02.415
 <i>-Thanks.</i>
 <i>-Welcome.</i>

34:02.457 --> 34:04.876
 <i>Uh, okay, Longhorn Diner?</i>

34:04.917 --> 34:07.045
 <i>Yeah, I can be there</i>
 <i>in about an hour.</i>

34:08.087 --> 34:09.338
 <i>Shit.</i>

34:12.425 --> 34:15.386
 <i>[slowed, heavy breathing</i>
 <i>of horse]</i>

34:15.428 --> 34:17.680
 <i> pensive music continues </i>

34:27.440 --> 34:28.941
 <i>[Faraday] Where I am from,</i>

34:30.777 --> 34:32.570
 <i>she was a predator.</i>

34:32.612 --> 34:34.822
 <i>Predator?</i>

34:34.864 --> 34:37.075
 <i>They're paintball practice</i>
 <i>if they ain't fast enough.</i>

34:39.035 --> 34:40.244
 <i>Paintball.</i>

34:40.787 --> 34:41.788
 <i>Yeah, man.</i>

34:42.705 --> 34:44.499
 <i>We let 'em run around,</i>

34:44.540 --> 34:45.666
 <i>then we shoot at 'em.</i>

34:50.713 --> 34:51.798
 <i>No.</i>

34:53.382 --> 34:54.842
 <i>No paintball.</i>

34:56.469 --> 34:59.430
 <i>That is not what she is for.</i>

35:15.071 --> 35:16.864
 <i>What's she for?</i>

35:16.906 --> 35:19.033
 <i>Soon she will remember.</i>

35:19.075 --> 35:20.535
 <i>Remember what?</i>

35:20.576 --> 35:22.745
 <i>She can kick that boy</i>
 <i>to death.</i>

35:28.668 --> 35:29.710
 <i>[Justin] We're, uh...</i>

35:29.752 --> 35:31.212
 <i>We're gonna make</i>
 <i>a quick stop, okay?</i>

35:31.254 --> 35:33.589
 <i>-We have three hours.</i>
 <i>-Yeah, we'll make it.</i>

35:33.631 --> 35:35.633
 <i>-It's okay. It's okay.</i>
 <i>-[garbled chatter on radio]</i>

35:39.178 --> 35:40.304
 <i>Is that your message?</i>

35:40.346 --> 35:42.598
 <i>Not close enough.</i>

35:42.640 --> 35:43.641
 <i>You know, you fell asleep</i>

35:43.683 --> 35:45.560
 <i>in the middle</i>
 <i>of a sentence before.</i>

35:45.601 --> 35:47.979
 <i>I was not asleep.</i>

35:48.020 --> 35:51.482
 <i>I was resting my eyes.</i>

35:51.524 --> 35:53.860
 <i>Yeah, men always say that.</i>
 <i>[chuckles]</i>

35:56.445 --> 35:58.322
 <i>[mimicking Josiah]</i>
 <i>Juzzie, Marcus was late.</i>

35:58.364 --> 36:00.158
 <i>When are you coming home?</i>

36:00.199 --> 36:03.995
 <i>Juzzie, my hands are aching.</i>
 <i>I need my pills. Juzzie.</i>

36:04.036 --> 36:05.496
 <i>[tires screech]</i>

36:06.747 --> 36:08.666
 <i>[car horn blaring]</i>

36:08.708 --> 36:11.335
 <i>Did you just mock him?</i>

36:11.377 --> 36:13.379
 <i>-Did you just mock my father?</i>
 <i>-[car horn blaring]</i>

36:13.421 --> 36:15.047
 <i>[man yells indistinctly]</i>

36:15.089 --> 36:16.132
 <i>How'd you do that?</i>

36:16.174 --> 36:17.550
 <i>You were asleep.</i>
 <i>How'd you hear him?</i>

36:17.592 --> 36:19.093
 <i>-[car horn blaring]</i>
 <i>-I was not sleeping.</i>

36:19.135 --> 36:20.303
 <i>[woman] Eat shit, asshole!</i>

36:20.344 --> 36:22.013
 <i>-[person yells indistinctly]</i>
 <i>-[honks horn]</i>

36:23.806 --> 36:25.057
 <i>I don't care about the money.</i>

36:25.099 --> 36:27.602
 <i>Apologize right now</i>
 <i>or I will lock these doors</i>

36:27.643 --> 36:29.103
 <i>and we will sit here</i>
 <i>in this truck</i>

36:29.145 --> 36:30.813
 <i>until we both wither and die.</i>

36:30.855 --> 36:33.024
 <i>-Three hours...</i>
 <i>-Oh, for fuck...</i>

36:33.065 --> 36:35.651
 <i>...28 minutes,</i>

36:35.693 --> 36:41.032
 <i>12 seconds,</i>
 <i>11 seconds, ten seconds,</i>

36:41.073 --> 36:43.201
 <i>-nine seconds...</i>
 <i>-[Justin sighs]</i>

36:43.242 --> 36:45.953
 <i>...eight seconds,</i>
 <i>seven seconds...</i>

36:45.995 --> 36:47.371
 <i>[whispering] Oh, my God.</i>

36:47.413 --> 36:49.540
 <i>-...six seconds...</i>
 <i>-[sighs]</i>

36:49.582 --> 36:53.711
 <i>[whispering]</i>
 <i>...five seconds, four seconds,</i>

36:53.753 --> 36:56.297
 <i>three seconds, two...</i>

36:56.339 --> 36:57.965
 <i>-My dad's sick.</i>
 <i>-...seconds,</i>

36:58.007 --> 37:00.301
 <i>one second.</i>

37:00.343 --> 37:03.304
 <i>He's fucking dying</i>
 <i>and we lost our coverage!</i>

37:03.346 --> 37:05.723
 <i>I get him his pills</i>
 <i>from a dealer</i>

37:05.765 --> 37:08.351
 <i>because that's the only way</i>
 <i>we can afford them.</i>

37:10.019 --> 37:12.188
 <i>That's why we're stopping.</i>

37:12.230 --> 37:17.318
 <i>My window of interception</i>
 <i>is shrinking.</i>

37:17.360 --> 37:19.946
 <i>Look, this is</i>
 <i>my mission, okay?</i>

37:19.987 --> 37:21.447
 <i>Keeping him comfortable,</i>

37:21.489 --> 37:22.990
 <i>or whatever the hell</i>
 <i>that means,</i>

37:23.032 --> 37:24.200
 <i>for as long as I can.</i>

37:24.242 --> 37:26.077
 <i>So, you can,</i>
 <i>[smacks lips] I don't know,</i>

37:26.118 --> 37:27.662
 <i>you know, find another ride.</i>

37:27.703 --> 37:30.164
 <i>Or you can choose</i>
 <i>to come with me.</i>

37:30.206 --> 37:32.250
 <i>-Those are your options.</i>
 <i>-[engine starts]</i>

37:33.584 --> 37:35.419
 <i>["Make Me Feel Alright" playing]</i>

37:43.803 --> 37:44.845
 <i>Stay.</i>

37:46.555 --> 37:47.640
 <i>[entry bell jingles]</i>

37:48.474 --> 37:49.600
 <i>[entry bell jingles]</i>

37:49.642 --> 37:51.269
 <i>[patrons chattering]</i>

37:52.728 --> 37:55.481
 <i>Hey, what are you doing?</i>
 <i>I said, stay with the truck.</i>

37:56.899 --> 37:57.942
 <i>[Justin sighs]</i>

37:59.235 --> 38:00.528
 <i>[bell dings]</i>

38:00.569 --> 38:02.446
 <i>Don't get all up on me</i>
 <i>like that.</i>

38:02.488 --> 38:04.907
 <i>You're like a baby duck. Sit.</i>

38:08.160 --> 38:09.495
 <i>[waitress] Hi! Coffee?</i>

38:09.537 --> 38:10.705
 <i>Yes, please.</i>

38:10.746 --> 38:12.373
 <i>Water, now.</i>

38:12.415 --> 38:14.125
 <i>I'm sorry. [chuckles]</i>

38:16.794 --> 38:17.795
 <i>Thank you.</i>

38:18.379 --> 38:20.298
 <i>[clock ticking]</i>

38:24.719 --> 38:27.305
 <i>[ambient noise's volume</i>
 <i>increases]</i>

38:29.890 --> 38:31.892
 <i>[bell dinging]</i>

38:31.934 --> 38:33.144
 <i>[man] Order up!</i>

38:36.188 --> 38:38.482
 <i>Their pheromones</i>
 <i>are giving me a headache.</i>

38:38.983 --> 38:40.026
 <i>[chuckles]</i>

38:40.067 --> 38:41.152
 <i>[groans]</i>

38:48.951 --> 38:51.329
 <i>Sorry about that. Sorry.</i>

38:51.370 --> 38:53.164
 <i>[sighs] Okay, listen to me.</i>

38:53.205 --> 38:56.167
 <i>Yeah, for right now,</i>
 <i>I need you to be less, okay?</i>

38:56.208 --> 38:58.461
 <i>Can you try to smile, maybe?</i>

38:58.502 --> 39:01.088
 <i>Oh, God. It's like something</i>
 <i>from a horror movie.</i>

39:01.130 --> 39:02.923
 <i>Don't do that.</i>
 <i>Don't do it. Stop.</i>

39:04.508 --> 39:06.677
 <i>-Listen...</i>
 <i>-He's on the spectrum.</i>

39:07.261 --> 39:08.929
 <i>I'm really sorry.</i>

39:08.971 --> 39:10.306
 <i>-Okay.</i>
 <i>-Thank you.</i>

39:10.348 --> 39:13.809
 <i>What is the spectrum?</i>

39:15.603 --> 39:17.271
 <i>It means that, you know,</i>

39:17.313 --> 39:19.940
 <i>you have different social</i>
 <i>and communication skills</i>

39:19.982 --> 39:21.108
 <i>to other people.</i>

39:21.150 --> 39:22.693
 <i>It means you can't connect.</i>

39:25.196 --> 39:26.238
 <i>Mm-mm.</i>

39:29.283 --> 39:30.409
 <i>Thank you.</i>

39:32.536 --> 39:35.373
 <i>You believe you are connected,</i>

39:35.414 --> 39:36.916
 <i>but you are not.</i>

39:36.957 --> 39:40.169
 <i>You exist only</i>
 <i>within yourselves.</i>

39:41.128 --> 39:43.005
 <i>And what makes you</i>
 <i>so different?</i>

39:43.047 --> 39:48.177
 <i>I am different because</i>
 <i>you are wasting my time.</i>

39:48.219 --> 39:51.597
 <i>I am not wasting your time.</i>

39:52.681 --> 39:55.935
 <i>When will Josiah Falls die?</i>

39:59.897 --> 40:01.399
 <i>Can I have</i>
 <i>two chocolate donuts,</i>

40:01.440 --> 40:02.441
 <i>-please?</i>
 <i>-Sure.</i>

40:03.776 --> 40:06.404
 <i>My dad used to do math</i>
 <i>to calm himself.</i>

40:06.445 --> 40:07.780
 <i>Is that what you're doing?</i>

40:09.740 --> 40:10.741
 <i>Thanks.</i>

40:14.787 --> 40:17.415
 <i>This is... This is base 60.</i>

40:17.456 --> 40:19.834
 <i>It's a third millennium</i>
 <i>number system.</i>

40:19.875 --> 40:21.419
 <i>What are you? I mean...</i>

40:21.460 --> 40:23.045
 <i>Are you an ancient Sumerian?</i>
 <i>I mean...</i>

40:23.087 --> 40:25.423
 <i>Why do you understand</i>
 <i>the value of base 60?</i>

40:25.464 --> 40:28.551
 <i>My adept.</i>

40:28.592 --> 40:31.554
 <i>You mean your teacher?</i>
 <i>Does your adept have a name?</i>

40:31.595 --> 40:35.808
 <i>Here, he is called</i>

40:37.768 --> 40:42.273
 <i>Thomas Jerome Newton.</i>

40:42.314 --> 40:43.941
 <i>-Thomas Jerome...</i>
 <i>-Yeah, I got it, babes.</i>

40:43.983 --> 40:46.610
 <i>-I got it.</i>
 <i>-...Newton.</i>

40:46.652 --> 40:49.822
 <i>[Justin] "Thomas Newton was the</i>
 <i>founder of World Enterprises."</i>

40:50.364 --> 40:51.449
 <i>That's it?</i>

40:52.283 --> 40:53.659
 <i>I mean, I... I heard about it.</i>

40:53.701 --> 40:56.412
 <i>It was a tech company,</i>
 <i>like, 40 years ago.</i>

40:56.454 --> 40:58.664
 <i>He is the one</i>
 <i>who sent me to you.</i>

40:58.706 --> 40:59.748
 <i>[scoffs]</i>

41:01.667 --> 41:03.127
 <i>What, this man?</i>

41:03.919 --> 41:05.504
 <i>You know this man?</i>

41:06.839 --> 41:09.967
 <i>Okay, and why</i>
 <i>would he do that?</i>

41:10.009 --> 41:15.764
 <i>Your work.</i>
 <i>You are vital to the mission.</i>

41:15.806 --> 41:19.059
 <i>Where I am from,</i>
 <i>there are two chambers.</i>

41:19.101 --> 41:21.145
 <i>Adepts and drones.</i>

41:21.187 --> 41:24.398
 <i>-One designs, one executes.</i>
 <i>-And...</i>

41:24.440 --> 41:27.151
 <i>Where are you from exactly?</i>

41:27.193 --> 41:30.988
 <i>-You used to produce more.</i>
 <i>-[entry bell jingles]</i>

41:31.030 --> 41:35.910
 <i>Your work now,</i>
 <i>what purpose does it serve?</i>

41:36.744 --> 41:38.454
 <i>It serves my purpose.</i>

41:38.496 --> 41:42.124
 <i>You are not utilizing</i>
 <i>your purpose.</i>

41:44.210 --> 41:47.046
 <i>Stay. I mean it.</i>

41:55.346 --> 41:56.889
 <i>You chose the correct task</i>

41:56.931 --> 41:58.390
 <i>but you did not have</i>
 <i>the tools.</i>

41:58.432 --> 41:59.892
 <i>Go outside.</i>

41:59.934 --> 42:02.436
 <i>-Go away, now.</i>
 <i>-The fuck you say to me?</i>

42:02.478 --> 42:03.687
 <i>I require her focus</i>

42:03.729 --> 42:06.148
 <i>and my window of interception</i>
 <i>is shrinking.</i>

42:06.190 --> 42:08.692
 <i>You are vital to the mission.</i>

42:08.734 --> 42:11.695
 <i>-Please stop talking.</i>
 <i>-You are vital.</i>

42:22.373 --> 42:24.124
 <i>[engine revs]</i>

42:27.586 --> 42:28.712
 <i>[engine revs]</i>

42:28.754 --> 42:31.173
 <i>[whispering] Shit. Shit!</i>

42:31.215 --> 42:33.217
 <i>[breath trembling]</i>

42:35.886 --> 42:37.763
 <i>Shit. Fuck.</i>

42:41.767 --> 42:43.769
 <i>[siren wailing]</i>

42:46.605 --> 42:47.606
 <i>Oh, shit.</i>

42:58.617 --> 43:00.035
 <i>[gasps]</i>

43:01.245 --> 43:02.746
 <i>[sighing in relief]</i>

43:04.373 --> 43:07.418
 <i>You know what?</i>
 <i>I don't want this anymore.</i>

43:09.420 --> 43:11.672
 <i>We have to get to 28.09...</i>

43:11.714 --> 43:12.840
 <i>There is no "we."</i>

43:12.881 --> 43:15.926
 <i>My mission is your mission.</i>

43:15.968 --> 43:17.678
 <i>What happened to you?</i>

43:18.470 --> 43:20.389
 <i>I mean, you're brilliant.</i>

43:20.431 --> 43:22.016
 <i>How'd you get here?</i>

43:22.057 --> 43:25.603
 <i>With a stranger</i>
 <i>in a strange place. How?</i>

43:25.644 --> 43:28.856
 <i>The adept miscalculated.</i>

43:28.897 --> 43:30.941
 <i>Miscalculated what?</i>
 <i>Be specific.</i>

43:30.983 --> 43:32.276
 <i>Energy.</i>

43:32.318 --> 43:34.069
 <i>Energy for what?</i>

43:34.111 --> 43:39.033
 <i>The energy we needed</i>
 <i>to save ourselves.</i>

43:42.661 --> 43:43.996
 <i>Did anyone, uh...</i>

43:45.497 --> 43:46.624
 <i>Did anyone die?</i>

43:47.666 --> 43:48.709
 <i>Yes.</i>

43:54.173 --> 43:55.174
 <i>Do... Do you have anyone?</i>

43:55.215 --> 43:57.593
 <i>I mean,</i>
 <i>besides the Newton guy?</i>

43:57.635 --> 44:00.554
 <i>A family, who takes care</i>
 <i>of you? Children?</i>

44:02.139 --> 44:03.265
 <i>Yes.</i>

44:05.017 --> 44:06.101
 <i>How many children?</i>

44:07.436 --> 44:08.479
 <i>Two.</i>

44:11.357 --> 44:14.652
 <i>They are waiting for me</i>
 <i>to return.</i>

44:18.781 --> 44:20.949
 <i>If they survived.</i>

44:24.536 --> 44:25.704
 <i>Survived what?</i>

44:30.709 --> 44:32.836
 <i>When the clouds disappear,</i>

44:34.546 --> 44:36.757
 <i>you all disappear.</i>

44:39.134 --> 44:41.887
 <i>You have</i>
 <i>very little time left.</i>

44:51.021 --> 44:53.857
 <i>-[Faraday] There! Stop there.</i>
 <i>-What? Here?</i>

44:54.900 --> 44:56.110
 <i>[Faraday] We have arrived.</i>

45:11.333 --> 45:13.085
 <i>[Justin]</i>
 <i>This doesn't feel right.</i>

45:13.961 --> 45:15.379
 <i>It is right.</i>

45:19.633 --> 45:21.635
 <i>You are afraid, I can...</i>

45:21.677 --> 45:23.220
 <i>-Smell it, I know.</i>
 <i>-...smell it.</i>

45:24.513 --> 45:25.931
 <i>I am afraid.</i>

45:27.349 --> 45:29.184
 <i>But not for me.</i>

45:29.226 --> 45:31.895
 <i>Look, there are bad people</i>
 <i>out here.</i>

45:31.937 --> 45:34.732
 <i>You know, like,</i>
 <i>the guys who jumped you?</i>

45:34.773 --> 45:37.484
 <i>Will you let me take you</i>
 <i>to a hotel or a bus station?</i>

45:38.402 --> 45:40.320
 <i>It gets cold here at night.</i>

45:40.362 --> 45:42.906
 <i>[Faraday] I will not be here</i>
 <i>for the cold.</i>

45:44.116 --> 45:45.284
 <i>Please.</i>

45:46.618 --> 45:48.245
 <i>Will you let me take you</i>
 <i>someplace safe?</i>

45:48.287 --> 45:50.664
 <i>I am where</i>
 <i>I am supposed to be.</i>

45:54.293 --> 45:55.419
 <i>You...</i>

45:57.212 --> 45:59.465
 <i>are where you are</i>
 <i>supposed to be.</i>

46:00.215 --> 46:01.258
 <i>For what?</i>

46:01.300 --> 46:05.888
 <i>To ensure the survival</i>
 <i>of my species.</i>

46:06.889 --> 46:08.974
 <i>Which species?</i>

46:10.642 --> 46:13.020
 <i>I am from Anthea.</i>

46:13.061 --> 46:14.521
 <i>A terrestrial planet</i>

46:14.563 --> 46:16.815
 <i>on the border</i>
 <i>of the solar system.</i>

46:16.857 --> 46:18.859
 <i>I am here to receive</i>

46:18.901 --> 46:21.904
 <i>the next step</i>
 <i>of my instructions.</i>

46:23.447 --> 46:26.283
 <i>You are meant</i>
 <i>to come with me.</i>

46:26.325 --> 46:27.659
 <i>[chuckles]</i>

46:29.244 --> 46:30.746
 <i>[chuckles] Look,</i>

46:31.705 --> 46:33.290
 <i>I brought you here,</i>

46:33.332 --> 46:35.459
 <i>and that's as much</i>
 <i>as I'm gonna do.</i>

46:35.501 --> 46:38.754
 <i>I'm not... I'm not going</i>
 <i>anywhere with you, okay?</i>

46:38.796 --> 46:41.131
 <i>All right? That's it.</i>
 <i>We're done here.</i>

46:41.173 --> 46:42.633
 <i>[Faraday] No more waiting!</i>

46:42.674 --> 46:44.468
 <i>Listen, don't follow me, okay?</i>

46:44.510 --> 46:46.136
 <i>You're fucking crazy.</i>

46:46.178 --> 46:47.638
 <i>What are you... Stop!</i>

46:47.679 --> 46:49.306
 <i>-Come with me!</i>
 <i>-Stop!</i>

46:49.348 --> 46:51.391
 <i>[metal creaking, crunching]</i>

46:51.433 --> 46:52.476
 <i>Come with me!</i>

46:53.352 --> 46:54.353
 <i>Stop!</i>

46:57.356 --> 46:59.066
 <i>[engine starts]</i>

47:17.209 --> 47:19.211
 <i>[wind whistling]</i>

47:28.929 --> 47:29.972
 <i>Fuck.</i>

47:48.323 --> 47:49.783
 <i>[thunder rumbles]</i>

47:53.662 --> 47:54.705
 <i>Fuck.</i>

47:55.998 --> 47:57.040
 <i>Oh, shit.</i>

47:59.209 --> 48:01.211
 <i>[wind whistling]</i>

48:12.139 --> 48:14.308
 <i>[rumbling]</i>

48:14.349 --> 48:16.560
 <i>-[crashing]</i>
 <i>-[wind gusting]</i>

48:24.484 --> 48:25.569
 <i>Shit!</i>

48:27.654 --> 48:28.697
 <i>Fuck!</i>

48:29.489 --> 48:31.450
 <i>[tires screech]</i>

48:34.995 --> 48:37.372
 <i>[wind gusting violently]</i>

48:58.477 --> 49:00.437
 <i>Fuck. Fuck.</i>

49:04.566 --> 49:06.610
 <i>[honking horn]</i>

49:12.866 --> 49:14.284
 <i>[car horn blares]</i>

49:17.204 --> 49:18.372
 <i>Faraday!</i>

49:22.876 --> 49:24.086
 <i>Far--</i>

49:29.341 --> 49:30.342
 <i>Shit.</i>

49:31.510 --> 49:33.512
 <i>-[car rattling]</i>
 <i>-[yells]</i>

49:36.348 --> 49:37.474
 <i>Fuck.</i>

49:39.393 --> 49:41.144
 <i>Fuck. Stop!</i>

49:41.687 --> 49:43.689
 <i>[screaming]</i>

49:58.161 --> 49:59.830
 <i>[whirring]</i>

50:05.043 --> 50:07.421
 <i>[whirring intensifying]</i>

50:21.059 --> 50:22.102
 <i>[whirring stops]</i>

50:24.896 --> 50:26.773
 <i>[man]</i> <i>Open your eyes.</i>

50:27.399 --> 50:29.192
 <i>[insects chirping]</i>

50:32.779 --> 50:34.614
 <i>[indistinct voices whispering]</i>

50:36.533 --> 50:37.993
 <i>[gasps]</i>

50:38.035 --> 50:40.078
 <i>[distant voice]</i>
 <i>Open your eyes.</i>

50:46.918 --> 50:48.211
 <i>[insects chitter]</i>

50:52.132 --> 50:54.009
 <i>[echoing whisper]</i> <i>It's me.</i>

51:00.474 --> 51:01.808
<i>Me.</i>

51:02.601 --> 51:03.894
<i>It's me.</i>

51:08.732 --> 51:11.610
<i>It's about fucking time.</i>
 <i>[continues echoing]</i>

51:17.240 --> 51:20.577
 <i>I know exactly</i>
 <i>what you're thinking.</i>

51:21.912 --> 51:24.206
 <i>"This is not the Anthean</i>
 <i>I remember."</i>

51:24.247 --> 51:27.918
 <i>Well, soon enough,</i>

51:27.959 --> 51:31.129
 <i>you won't be the Anthean</i>
 <i>you remember, either.</i>

51:32.798 --> 51:35.258
 <i>But I'm gonna make you</i>

51:36.301 --> 51:40.222
 <i>the god they can't ignore.</i>

51:41.306 --> 51:42.641
 <i>[laughing]</i>

51:45.102 --> 51:47.104
 <i>[continues laughing]</i>

51:55.153 --> 51:56.530
 <i>[Faraday]</i> <i>How did we get here?</i>

51:59.658 --> 52:01.034
<i>To this place.</i>

52:02.494 --> 52:03.620
 <i>In this box,</i>

52:03.662 --> 52:06.289
 <i>I hold the next step</i>
 <i>on the great timeline.</i>

52:06.331 --> 52:10.418
 <i>I am a tyrant. I am the king!</i>
 <i>Tech god. Willy Wonka.</i>

52:10.460 --> 52:13.672
 <i>Up to my Gobstoppers</i>
 <i>in secrets.</i>

52:16.174 --> 52:17.717
 <i>And it's all true.</i>

52:19.177 --> 52:20.303
 <i>Well,</i>

52:21.179 --> 52:23.390
 <i>the secrets part, anyway.</i>

52:25.684 --> 52:27.352
 <i>So, don't say</i>
 <i>I didn't warn you.</i>
